Company: ${companyName}
Balance Sheet as of: ${reportEndDate}
Report Generated: ${reportDate}

Assets:
<jx:forEach items="${assetItems}" var="item" >
${item.name} ${item.amount}
</jx:forEach>
Total Assets: ${totalAssets}

Liabilities:
<jx:forEach items="${liabilityItems}" var="item" >
${item.name} ${item.amount}
</jx:forEach>
Total Liabilities: ${totalLiabilities}

Equity:
<jx:forEach items="${equityItems}" var="item" >
${item.name} ${item.amount}
</jx:forEach>
Current Period Net Income: ${currentPeriodNetIncome}
Total Equity: ${totalEquity} (Note: Includes Current Period Net Income)

Total Liabilities and Equity: ${totalLiabilitiesAndEquity}

Verification: Assets == L+E ? ${assetsEqualsLiabilitiesPlusEquity}
